(40, 7, 17, 19, 92, 13, 14, NULL, 'Fruitfulness in God''s Presence', 'Both passages emphasize the idea of producing good fruit as a sign of being rooted in God. Matthew highlights that good trees yield good fruit, while Psalms speaks of those planted in the house of the Lord continuing to bear fruit.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
